{
  "stem": "11133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, at first, lived in one of those buildings that faced to the outside of the ghetto-- so we could see some of the trees and things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then they moved us out of that house, because that house then became part of the outside of the ghetto, into more inner-- say, I think we moved twice, two or three times within the ghetto-- each time to a smaller accommodation.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Each time to share with more people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, you would have one room, and there would be another family in another room, and everybody would be sharing the kitchen and the hallway and the bathrooms.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Life just became totally different, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we still had-- well, right away, as I remember, they closed all the bank accounts, you know, Jewish bank accounts were closed.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my parents couldn't withdraw any money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I'm sure that knowing the war was coming, I think everybody sort of put some money away, and some.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think they sold a few valuables things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, they got some money for the furniture, and-- I assume.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I mean, I didn't question them at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But now in retrospect, I would imagine that that's where the money came from and that that's how we paid for food, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Jews tend to be survivors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What else do you remember about the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember-- you know, as a child in the ghetto, at first, it was not-- for a child, we were then squished together in a tight place, but there were lots of other children.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in a sense, there was more time to play.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
